{"tid":1051798,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（厲害了）中共軍媒指士兵未能適應新裝備　演習頻失誤","createTime":"2019-03-08T00:58:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T01:26:42.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d421c59da75a0757b8c9f4c445e73c3cf4551e26","tid":1051798,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T00:58:21.000Z","msg":"內地有軍方背景的《解放軍報》早前發表的文章，當中寫到解放軍去年演習頻頻出現失誤，包括地面部隊演習中，出現攻方內部的偵察網絡數據傳送未能迅速發出，因而令步戰車暴露於敵方火力點前。報道同時將解放軍部隊數碼化後出現的問題歸因為人才問題，引起外界關注。<br />\n<br />\n文章指出，事後軍方曾開檢討會，負責戰術演練的軍官表示，因攻方坦克及步戰車的信息數據要「在後方指揮所繞一大圈」才能發出，因而貽誤時機。惟該軍營營長指，事件原因不僅是能力問題，更在於觀念未轉變，認為未有提前建立信息互動的指揮網絡是主要原因。<br />\n<br />\n文章又指，解放軍部隊數碼化後有兩大問題，包括軍人未能適應武器裝備不斷升級，能力差距拉大；以及作戰模式加速轉變，但作戰觀念仍落伍。報道強調軍方人才需從技術型轉為專家型，但承認相關改變需時。<br />\n<br />\n早前英媒亦引述哈佛大學中國事務專家約翰斯頓指，僅在去年《解放軍報》就曾提及了數百次「軍力薄弱」的字眼。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190305/mobile/bkn-20190305120135111-0305_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190305%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190305120135111-0305_00952_001.html&d=%2BySIvleuZbSdMWEfOjMUQsQ0GhOv7yEvjYTsEPvBCF8%3D&h=262addf2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190305/mobile/bkn-20190305120135111-0305_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a9e155b4741314ece7385d147349b388072beec8","tid":1051798,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T01:00:08.000Z","msg":"未能適應裝備升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cdd901deb342b1e1dc394ef155dd1b63c107162","tid":1051798,"uid":522,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T01:10:56.000Z","msg":"球場草地太硬"},{"pid":"3512d32b6417c306ccc3dc628f2b0e3613a07418","tid":1051798,"uid":162221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T01:14:21.000Z","msg":"中國幾十年唔打仗<br />\n<br />\n當美國創造打仗嘅趨勢<br />\n中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5761549e32d1db12fab9bd71b9cc8b29872479b","tid":1051798,"uid":53026,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"3512d32b6417c306ccc3dc628f2b0e3613a07418","tid":1051798,"uid":162221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T01:14:21.000Z","msg":"中國幾十年唔打仗<br />\n<br />\n當美國創造打仗嘅趨勢<br />\n中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T01:22:23.000Z","msg":"對上一次出坦克車係三十年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且唔係打仗"},{"pid":"450a0fb44e30c90a29f243ec7dfe0c205c7426a4","tid":1051798,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T01:23:18.000Z","msg":"支那仲用緊弓箭？"},{"pid":"8e55655c0b5dcfd3cfe9f846504c85f8c0b0568b","tid":1051798,"uid":24752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T01:23:23.000Z","msg":"咩新裝備？摺被機？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbe799600456c7fda2e17bba46f0cc06a4e19fe3","tid":1051798,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T01:26:42.000Z","msg":"出現攻方內部的偵察網絡數據傳送未能迅速發出<br />\n<br />\n5G呢? 華為呢?"}]}